{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T10:52:21.575Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "Hidden State — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What Hidden State Is"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "hidden state"}, {"type": "text", "text": " in Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) is the network's "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "internal memory"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that stores information about everything it has seen in the sequence up to the current time step. It acts as a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "running summary"}, {"type": "text", "text": " or compressed representation of all previous inputs, allowing the network to maintain context and understand sequential relationships."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mathematically, it's a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "vector (list of numbers)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " that captures historical information of the sequence up to time step "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ". "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://d2l.ai/chapter_recurrent-neural-networks/rnn.html", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "d2l"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why Hidden State Matters in Generative AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The hidden state is the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "critical component"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that enables RNNs to process sequential data effectively in generative AI:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Importance"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Application"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Context retention"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Chatbots maintain conversation context across multiple turns"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Sequential understanding"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Text generation maintains story coherence over long passages"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Variable-length sequences"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Process sentences, paragraphs, or documents of any length"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Pattern learning"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Learn relationships that unfold over time (language, music, time series)"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Without hidden state, the network would \"forget everything after each step, making it impossible to understand context\"."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How Hidden State Works (Core Mechanics)"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The update formula:"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "At each time step "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ", the hidden state is computed based on:\n1. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Current input"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "x_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n2. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Previous hidden state"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_{t-1}"}}]}, {"type": "blockMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_t = f(x_t, h_{t-1})"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "f"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " is typically a nonlinear activation function like tanh."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "More specifically:"}]}, {"type": "blockMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_t = \\tanh(W_{xh} \\cdot x_t + W_{hh} \\cdot h_{t-1} + b_h)"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where:\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "W_{xh}"}}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": " = weight matrix for input-to-hidden connections\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "W_{hh}"}}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": " = weight matrix for hidden-to-hidden (recurrent) connections\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "b_h"}}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": " = bias term"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The flow through time:"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "yaml"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Time step t=0:\n  Input: x₀ (first word)\n  Previous state: h₀ (initial state = 0 vector)\n  New state: h₁ = f(x₀, h₀)\n  Output: y₀ based on h₁\n\nTime step t=1:\n  Input: x₁ (second word)\n  Previous state: h₁ (from before)\n  New state: h₂ = f(x₁, h₁)\n  Output: y₁ based on h₂\n\nTime step t=2:\n  Input: x₂ (third word)\n  Previous state: h₂ (from before)\n  New state: h₃ = f(x₂, h₂)\n  Output: y₂ based on h₃"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The hidden state is "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "passed forward"}, {"type": "text", "text": " to the next time step, acting as the network's memory of what it has seen so far."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Characteristics of Hidden State"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "1. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Acts as connection between time steps"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The hidden state "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " is the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "critical link"}, {"type": "text", "text": " connecting time steps, allowing information to flow through the sequence."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "2. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Depends on all previous inputs"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The hidden state at time "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " depends on:\n- The current input "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "x_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- The hidden state from time "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "t-1"}}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- Which itself depended on "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "x_{t-1}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " and "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_{t-2}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- And so on..."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "This means "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " holds details from "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "all previous inputs"}, {"type": "text", "text": " "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "x_1, x_2,..., x_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ", not just the last one."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "3. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Dynamic memory"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The hidden state is like "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "dynamic memory that updates at each step"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", combining new input with past information."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "4. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Short-term vs. Long-term"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Vanilla RNN"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Hidden state is short-term memory (prone to forgetting)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "LSTM"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Has both hidden state "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " (short-term) and cell state "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "C_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " (long-term memory) "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://d2l.ai/chapter_recurrent-neural-networks/rnn.html", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "d2l"}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Hidden State vs. Output"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Property"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Hidden State ("}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ")"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Output ("}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "y_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ")"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Purpose"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Memory for next time step"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Prediction/result at current step"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Passed to"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Next time step ("}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "t+1"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ")"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "User/model consumer"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Content"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Summary of all past inputs"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Decision based on current state + input"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Analogy"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Factors causing the output"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The predicted price/value"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Example"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Predicting stock prices:\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Output at day 1000"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Predicted price at day 1000\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "State at day 1000"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Factors causing that output (season, volatility, market sentiment) encoded numerically"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Benefits of Hidden State"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Benefit"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Explanation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Memory through time"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Stores information across sequence elements"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Context propagation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Carries context forward to influence future outputs"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Sequential modeling"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Enables understanding of order-dependent patterns"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Variable-length handling"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Process sequences of any length without fixed input size"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Historical information"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Captures sequence history up to current time step "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://d2l.ai/chapter_recurrent-neural-networks/rnn.html", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "d2l"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Trade-offs & Limitations"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Limitation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Explanation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Vanishing gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Vanilla RNN hidden states lose information over long sequences"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Limited capacity"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Fixed-size vector must compress entire sequence history"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Information bottleneck"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Some details may be lost when compressing long sequences"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Short-term focus"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Vanilla RNNs tend to forget very old information"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Solutions: Advanced Cells"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Cell Type"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How It Improves Hidden State"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "LSTM"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Adds gating mechanisms to control what to retain/discard"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "GRU"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Simplified gating for better long-term memory"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "LSTM"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Separates short-term ("}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ") and long-term ("}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "C_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ") memory "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://d2l.ai/chapter_recurrent-neural-networks/rnn.html", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "d2l"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Advanced RNN variants like LSTM and GRU improve the process by "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "controlling what information to retain or discard"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", helping manage longer sequences."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Hidden State in RNN Architecture"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Basic RNN structure:"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "yaml"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Input Sequence: [word₁, word₂, word₃, ...]\n                    ↓\n              [Recurrent Cell]\n     Input: x₀  →  h₀ = 0 (initial)\n     Output: h₁ = f(x₀, h₀)\n                    ↓\n              [Recurrent Cell]\n     Input: x₁  →  h₁ (from before)\n     Output: h₂ = f(x₁, h₁)\n                    ↓\n              [Recurrent Cell]\n     Input: x₂  →  h₂ (from before)\n     Output: h₃ = f(x₂, h₂)\n                    ↓\n                  ..."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each cell produces a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "new hidden state"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that is passed to the next time step."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "With output layer:"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Hidden state h_t\n        ↓\n  [Output Layer]\n        ↓\n    Output y_t = softmax(W_{hy} · h_t + b_y)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The output is typically computed from the hidden state using an activation function like softmax for classification."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mental Model"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Think of the hidden state as a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "person's working memory while reading a book"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "At word 1"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (\"The\"): Hidden state = [\"someone is starting a sentence\"]"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "At word 2"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (\"cat\"): Hidden state = [\"someone is talking about a cat\"]"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "At word 3"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (\"sits\"): Hidden state = [\"a cat is doing something, sitting\"]"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "At word 4"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (\"on\"): Hidden state = [\"cat is sitting on something, location coming\"]"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "At word 5"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (\"the\"): Hidden state = [\"cat is sitting on a specific object\"]"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "At word 6"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (\"mat\"): Hidden state = [\"complete sentence: The cat sits on the mat\"]"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each hidden state "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "accumulates context"}, {"type": "text", "text": " from all previous words, allowing the network to understand the full meaning."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Or think of it as a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "notebook"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- You write notes as you read each word\n- The notebook (hidden state) contains everything you've learned so far\n- At each step, you read the new word and update your notes\n- The notebook persists across time, carrying information forward"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Example: Text Generation"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Imagine generating text: \"I love to "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}, {"type": "italic"}], "text": "\""}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "yaml"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Step 1: Input \"I\"\n  h₁ = f(\"I\", h₀=0)\n  h₁ encodes: [subject starting]\n\nStep 2: Input \"love\"\n  h₂ = f(\"love\", h₁)\n  h₂ encodes: [subject + positive emotion]\n\nStep 3: Input \"to\"\n  h₃ = f(\"to\", h₂)\n  h₃ encodes: [subject + positive emotion + action coming]\n\nStep 4: Predict next word\n  y₃ = softmax(h₃)\n  Output: \"code\" (because h₃ suggests action verb)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The hidden state accumulates context so the model can predict coherent next words."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Takeaways"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Hidden state"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is RNN's internal memory vector storing everything seen up to the current time step"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "It's a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "running summary"}, {"type": "text", "text": " of all previous inputs, enabling context retention"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Updated at each step: "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_t = f(x_t, h_{t-1})"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ", combining current input with past memory "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://d2l.ai/chapter_recurrent-neural-networks/rnn.html", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "d2l"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Depends on all previous inputs"}, {"type": "text", "text": " "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "x_1,..., x_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ", not just the last one"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Acts as the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "connection between time steps"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", allowing information to flow through sequences"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Without hidden state"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", RNNs would forget everything after each step, making context understanding impossible"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Vanilla RNNs"}, {"type": "text", "text": " have short-term hidden states (prone to forgetting); "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "LSTMs"}, {"type": "text", "text": " add long-term cell state "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "C_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://d2l.ai/chapter_recurrent-neural-networks/rnn.html", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "d2l"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Essential for "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "text generation, chatbots, language modeling"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", and all sequential generative AI tasks"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The hidden state is what makes RNNs capable of "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "understanding sequences"}, {"type": "text", "text": "—it's the core that allows them to remember, learn patterns, and generate meaningful outputs."}]}]}}